text: Bhanidinus timiharu hamro barema juna kurako pratiksa garirakheka chau, tyo du'ita bhala'iharumadhye e'uta ho ra hami timro hakama pratiksa gardachaum ki ya ta allahale aphno tarphabata kunai yatana timila'i de'os va hamro hatabata, tasartha ekatira timi pratiksarata raha arkotira timro sathama hami pani pratiksarata chaum
